{"type": "article", "id": 29238, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-07-06T22:51:57Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 20787, "name": "Sweety & Co."}, {"id": 29871, "name": "Blå Station"}, {"id": 29872, "name": "De Vorm"}, {"id": 24611, "name": "Stefan Borselius"}, {"id": 29873, "name": "Ivan Kasner"}, {"id": 29874, "name": "Uli Budde"}, {"id": 29875, "name": "Malgorzata Mozolewska"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 23, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160706163655J2AeOtF16og7xpHj.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">          </p>\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<h3>AK 2 by Ivan Kasner &amp; Uli Budde</h3>\n<p>开放式的工作环境有时会让人无法保持专注的状态工作，也很难有效地保护隐私。<a href=\"http://www.ivankasner.nl/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ivan Kasner</a> 和 <a href=\"http://www.ulibudde.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Uli Budde</a> 为荷兰家具公司 <a href=\"http://www.devorm.nl/home\" rel=\"nofollow\">De Vorm</a> 设计了一块带灯饰的隔板 <a href=\"http://www.devorm.nl/products/ak-2-pet-felt-workspace-divider-lamp\" rel=\"nofollow\">AK 2</a>，两边分别装有 LED 灯，可以同时为两边的使用者提供稳定的照明。AK 2 所使用的毛毡由回收的 PET 瓶制作而成的，不仅质地柔软，对声音也有极强的吸附性，一定程度上可以减轻噪音干扰。AK 2 提供多种颜色选择，你可以通过<a href=\"http://www.devorm.nl/contact\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>与 De Vorm 联系购买。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706235152ocK3gy0PruaLGk2F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.986553\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706235153K2wfoSAg9j0vqPOR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.622249\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706235153juweifM4v5hTJ7Ay.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607062351536bFVnmYO80vBJaGA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.580685\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706235155EKCkqscVJBeZ06Wv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.248470\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h3>Pucca by Stefan Borselius</h3>\n<p>喜欢在房间里摆上软软的大坐垫？<a href=\"http://www.borselius.se/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Stefan Borselius</a> 为 Blå Station 设计的大坐垫和脚垫系列 <a href=\"http://www.blastation.com/products/news-2016/pucca/pucca-o541\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pucca</a> 会用它们圆鼓鼓的造型和温和的配色吸引你的注意力，有点像是放大版的马卡龙。考虑到人们时不时会在家里挪动这些结实的家具，Borselius 在一侧还特意安上了不锈钢的拉环，增强了可动性。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706235129aFI6Dny0GHJruV28.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.574219\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607062351283t86MGWlCaJw49Ui.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.330000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706235128N1FRo685Ums49tgM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.773333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706235128e0VRdnZyQADHUGoW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.416667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706235128W2gTUltoauVqsKnh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.435000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706235128B8je6W40vYRCzKGu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.555000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h3>Eye of the light by Studio MMozolewska</h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://mmozolewska.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Malgorzata Mozolewska</a> 以大自然中蝴蝶的翅膀和鸟儿的羽翼作为灵感，推出了 <a href=\"http://mmozolewska.com/projects/eye-of-the-light-2016/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Eye of the light</a> 灯具系列，灯罩部分看起来就像是一片片在风中飘扬的银色织物。Mozolewska 希望通过这个系列探索金属会如何呈现不同功能的家饰，轻盈多变的造型让 Eye of the light 能够呈现出不一样的光照效果，它既可以是吸睛的灯具，不亮灯时又能作为优雅的室内装饰品。Eye of the light 分为台灯、吊灯和落地灯三款，所有灯具都由来自波兰的工匠手工制成。这是它的<a href=\"http://shop.mmozolewska.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，价格从 525 到 2460 欧元不等。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706235049WiPsGKUwhdt4JAga.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.585000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706235049GdbITso1zy6ZNUwM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.670984\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706235049UwPyz8EGBQ7WpHn2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.740000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706235050SPvK6XBqRz0pd1bi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.100000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706235050hBEqogjF7bIHzdfx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706235050u19dKeghLbv80Fxr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.950000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h3>Stacked by Stacked</h3>\n<p>你眼中好用的接线板会有哪几个要素？最好配有多个插座，造型也要好看到至少不需要把它藏在角落里。我们之前就介绍过一款小巧的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/28931.html\">接线板</a>，不过它的插头可能对一些人来说并不够用。初创公司 <a href=\"http://stackedmodular.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Stacked</a> 选择一个聪明的办法，同名的接线板被设计为模块化的结构，人们可以根据需要自由地加减模块。由于每一节内部都采用了转轴的设计，还可以进行旋转，那些之前无法并排接入的插座终于可以同时使用了。除此之外，Stacked 还自带电压保护器和两个 USB 接口，能够满足大部分日常需求。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.stackedmodular.com/store/stacked-modular-power-strip.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 30 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706235016y7JmnqdYRcEbsC1K.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607062350062KJ01VWqUIo7bXwZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706235006CqF8NYBcT1JPQb3d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706235007ziaHvQWBrp4u9JoU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070623500849V1eIqorHLG3uRx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706235007wh6VXrQGzl8ZxJAt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h3>EDC Card Caddy by Hitch and Timber</h3>\n<p>无论是结账时翻找钱包还是在需要其他随身小物时苦寻不见，都是让人觉得手忙脚乱而且尴尬的时刻，美国品牌 <a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/HitchandTimber\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hitch and Timber</a> 推出了一款专门为日常小物而设计的小口袋 EDC Card Caddy，其中 EDC 正是 Everyday Carry 的缩写。它由巴尔的摩当地的工匠采用高级植鞣皮革手工制作而成，虽然外形有些粗旷但缝合处又不失细致。小巧的造型可以刚好放进衣物口袋，能够容纳最多五张卡片、小刀以及钢笔等小物。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/398923419/brown-edc-card-caddy-leather-card-wallet\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 46 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706234939PqcUDTQ7jVnEyZuJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706234939xIYkTArzgJGhKEP3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607062349393Cv59gHNdl2TWPce.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706234939d47KgcJ3mRba1rfA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607062349393xfmgw8vEYRrL57d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h3>RAWCHA by Sweety &amp; Co.</h3>\n<p>RAWCHA 是一个来自巴西的抹茶品牌，<a href=\"http://sweetyand.co/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Sweety &amp; Co.</a> 的设计师们在制品包装中采用了四种明亮的颜色与白色搭配排版，印上了各种原料和茶杯的小巧紧凑的图案，看上去轻快活泼。Sweety &amp; Co. 希望用这种风格与当地同类产品形成差异，用富有时尚感的基调吸引顾客。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706234913Tso9v6I1adVWtCQK.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.250000\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706234914tTJalchbCZBeoHEP.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.624000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706234913FMxRfbBPiNTpyqO4.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.610000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706234913X4GRk91rKmwzTvuW.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.767000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706234916p5zAZ04xf7tkYI9u.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.574000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160706234917OiQFkLgKvZ2RYf8d.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}